movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Sacrificing soul for marketability
review: Little baby greedos! Farting camels! A happy, cherubic Darth Vader! Cheerful alien sidekicks.Darth Vader's childhood should have been something more out of Omen than this crap, but Lucas needs to hit that crucial 8-11 year old age bloc, and here it is.
